#define R(p,a,t) mix(a*dot(p,a),p,cos(t))+sin(t)*cross(p,a)
#define H(h) (cos((h)*6.3+vec3(0,23,21))*.5+.5)

void mainImage(out vec4 O, vec2 C)
{
    vec3 p,r=iResolution,c=vec3(0),
    d=normalize(vec3((C-.5*r.xy)/r.y,1));
    float i=0.,s,e,g=0.,t=iTime;
	for(;i++<90.;){
        p=g*d;
        p.z-=15.+sin(t*.1)*2.;
        p=R(p,normalize(cos(t*.5+vec3(1,8,3))),clamp(sin(t*.2)*3.,-5.,.5));
        p=abs(p);
        vec4 p4=vec4(p,1),q4=p4;
        s=3.;
        for(int i=0;i++<6;)
            p4=1.-abs(abs(abs(p4-4.)-1.)-2.),
            s*=e=-18./min(dot(p4,p4),10.),
            p4=p4*e+q4;
        p4-=clamp(p4,-15.,15.);
        g+=e=length(p4)/s;
        c+=mix(vec3(1),H(log(s)*.3+t*.3),.4)*.012/exp(i*i*e);  
    }
    c*=c;
    O=vec4(c,1);
}
